Dependencies
------------

-  Server side

   -  `Flask-SQLAlchemy <https://flask-sqlalchemy.palletsprojects.com/en/2.x/>`__
   -  `Flask-Restless <https://flask-restless.readthedocs.io/en/stable/>`__

-  Client side

   -  `jsgrid <http://js-grid.com/>`__


